在Network节点上：

Bridge br-int
    Port patch-tun
        Interface patch-tun
            type: patch
            options: {peer=patch-int}
    Port "tapde5739e1-95"
        tag: 1
        Interface "tapde5739e1-95"
            type: internal
    Port br-int
        Interface br-int
            type: internal
    Port "qr-e8b97930-ac"
        tag: 1
        Interface "qr-e8b97930-ac"
            type: internal

非常相似的规则。

